OL,6,CG1979FThe first edition of The Paul
OL,7,FDaniels Magic Show airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,FRadio Times: "Join Paul Daniels for the
OL,10,Ffirst of four special programmes in
OL,11,Fwhich television's top comedy magic
OL,12,Fstar entertains in his own unusual
OL,13,Ffashion and introduces the remarkable
OL,14,Fskills of his guests."
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe programme ran for 15 years, with
OL,17,Fthe final show airing on BBC One on
OL,18,FSaturday 18th June 1994.
