OL,14,FTV Times: "At last! The Roxy, the venue
OL,15,Ffor ITV's new pop chart show, opens for
OL,16,Fbusiness. A galaxy of British and
OL,17,Finternational recording stars welcome
OL,18,Fthe arrival of the nation's glossiest
OL,19,Fand best showcase for up-to-the-minute
OL,20,Fmusic talent.
